Package io.openems.backend.alerting.scheduler

Class MinuteTimer

java.lang.Object
io.openems.backend.alerting.scheduler.MinuteTimer
All Implemented Interfaces:
TimedExecutor
Direct Known Subclasses:
MinuteTimerAsync
public class MinuteTimer extends Object implements TimedExecutor
Executes subscriber every full Minute or once after a specified time of Minutes. Starts and stops itself, depending on whether subscribers are present.
